text: Anita Filipovics (born 9 April 1988) is a Hungarian volleyball player. She played at the 2010 FIVB Volleyball Women's World Championship European qualification, and 2011 Women's European Volleyball League. In 2005, she was the Hungarian Women's Volleyball League champion, with Vasas SC.
